textfsm_template:
Value PORT (\S+)
Value TEMP (\S+)
Value VOLTAGE (\S+)
Value BIAS_CURRENT (\S+)
Value TX_POWER (\S+)
Value RX_POWER (\S+)


Start
  ^---- -> Begin

Begin
  ^${PORT}\s+${TEMP}\s+${VOLTAGE}\s+${BIAS_CURRENT}\s+${TX_POWER}\s+${RX_POWER}\s+(\S+ ago|N/A) -> Record
  ^\s+$$
  ^$$
  ^.* -> Error "LINE NOT FOUND"
  
EOF
